# Configuration file

general {
    # Determines whether or not the default tips should be possible. This includes tips added directly by other mods through their language files. [default: true]
    B:allowDefaultTips=false

    # A list of custom tips added by the user or modpack. [default: ]
    S:customTips <
    Asking terna to play this pack will result in failure.#SPLIT#Fun Fact
    You can hold left alt/right alt + a direction key to dash in that direction.#SPLIT#Did you know?
    If you ever need help, try using the quest book!
    Basic ores can not be smelted without the use of a smeltery.
    The Darkness can be deadly.#SPLIT#Did you know?
    Blazing pyrotheum can be used in a smeltery to speed up smelting.#SPLIT#Did you know?
    You will die.#SPLIT#Atum 2 tip
    Every few nights you may face a hostile invasion.
    You can craft different turrets to fight off mobs during the night.
    Some items may require you to read up on them before being able to be used.

    
     >

    # The color of the actual tip text. [default: FFFFFF]
    S:textColor=FFFFFF

    # The color of the top/title text for the tip. [default: FFFF55]
    S:titleColor=FFFF55

    # The amount of offset the tip text should have from the left of the screen. [range: 0 ~ 2147483647, default: 5]
    I:xOffset=5

    # The amount of offset the tip text should have from the bottom of the screen. [range: 0 ~ 2147483647, default: 40]
    I:yOffset=40
}


